cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with speech emotion recognition using deep learning techniques, which falls under the sub-categories of Speech and Signal Processing (cs.SD), Natural Language Processing (cs.CL), and Machine Learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). The use of Deep Belief Networks (DBNs) and Sparse Auto Encoder and SVM also suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI).
